thread.title: Jaime

author: Jaime
title: Jaime
text: Ordered a beauty trolley which arrived nice and quick! Fairly easy instructions to put the trolley together, but the trolley came with brown marks that I cannot get off. Really annoying as this is suppose to be brand new/unused. It is a white trolley so the marks can easily be seen. It also had a weird condensation/liquid in the packaged box. Would not purchase from here again as it is very disappointing
